goosemanager.name: GooseManager
goosemanager.author: JQ#1693
goosemanager.description: Manage Goose actions and speed tiers. Now you can finally disable your goose from bringing you memes without an error popping up! (2020 Samperson Mod Jam winner)
goosemanager.description-debug: (2020 Samperson Mod Jam winner!) Have you ever wanted to make your goose don't bring memes, notes or do nothing? Now you can! Adds a file where you can disable goose tasks/actions and another file for disabling goose speed (tiers). Or you can use ''configure mod'' option (click on the mod button and then you will see this option, if you can't click that option try reinstalling mod) Supports tasks/actions added by mods! How To Use Easy way out: Use ''configure mod'' option (click on the mod button and then you will see this option, if you can't click that option try reinstalling mod) disabling goose actions: After first time of starting goose with this mod, GooseTasks.txt file will be added to mod folder, there you can disable action by changing True to False on the right side of action name! If all actions are disabled, all actions will be enabled! disabling goose speed tiers: After first time of starting goose with this mod, GooseSpeedTiers.txt file will be added to mod folder, there you can disable speed tier by changing True to False on the right side of speed tier! If all speed tiers are disabled, all speed tiers will be enabled for everything: To apply changes you need to restart goose Attention! Having only charge active while having active meme and note actions will make goose dancing with window while holded window is on Disabling charge will not change goose speed in Nabmouse action (when goose catches mouse speed will change)
